---
// About section with stats
---

<section id="about" class="section about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="grid grid--2">
            <div class="about__content">
                <span class="badget">Sobre Nosotros</span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Más que un club, <br>una comunidad.</h2>
                <p class="section-desc">En Web Club Natación, fusionamos la técnica de alto rendimiento con un
                    ambiente acogedor. Nuestros entrenadores olímpicos diseñan programas personalizados para
                    cada nivel.</p>

                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number" data-target="15">0</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Años de Experticia</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number" data-target="500">0</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Miembros Activos</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about__image">
                <div class="image-reveal">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519315901367-f34ff9154487?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        alt="Swimmer underwater">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.about {
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
}

.about__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
}

.stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-md);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-bg-alt);
}

.stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
}

.stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
}

.stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-top: 5px;
}

.about__image {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
}

.about__image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 1.5s ease;
}

.about__image:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
}
</style>
